summary: This is a U.S. Customs and Border Protection Person Encounter Detail record documenting Ghislaine Maxwell's entry into the United States at Palm Beach International Airport on January 21, 2000. The record indicates she was processed as an inbound traveler and was not referred for secondary inspection.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: Documented as entering the United States at Palm Beach International Airport on January 21, 2000, via an inbound flight.

events.title: Ghislaine Maxwell's Entry to U.S.
events.description: Ghislaine Maxwell arrived in the United States via an inbound flight, processed by U.S. Customs and Border Protection at Palm Beach International Airport.

keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell entered the United States at Palm Beach International Airport on January 21, 2000, at 23:33 Eastern Time.
The document is a U.S. Customs and Border Protection Person Encounter Detail record, indicating official tracking of her travel.
Maxwell's arrival was processed as 'INBOUND' and she was 'NOT REFERRED' for secondary inspection.
The flight number was 505LS, though the departure and arrival locations beyond the airport are coded (00).
